sequenceDiagram
    actor Employee
    participant ApplyPage as SCREEN-LEAVE-APPLY
    participant LeaveAPI as API-LEAVE-CREATE
    participant LeaveTable as TABLE-LEAVE_REQUEST
    actor Manager
    participant ApprovalPage as SCREEN-LEAVE-APPROVAL
    participant ApprovalAPI as API-LEAVE-APPROVE
    participant ApprovalTable as TABLE-LEAVE_APPROVAL
    participant EventBus as EVT-LEAVE-APPROVED

    Employee->>ApplyPage: STEP-LEAVE-010 enter apply page
    ApplyPage->>ApplyPage: DEC-LEAVE-020 validate RULE-LEAVE-001/002/008
    ApplyPage->>ApplyPage: DEC-LEAVE-030 validate RULE-LEAVE-003/009
    ApplyPage->>LeaveAPI: STEP-LEAVE-040 submit UC-LEAVE-SUBMIT
    LeaveAPI->>LeaveTable: STEP-LEAVE-060 create pending request
    LeaveAPI-->>Employee: return requestId and STATE-REQUEST-PENDING
    Manager->>ApprovalPage: STEP-LEAVE-080 open approval worklist
    ApprovalPage->>ApprovalAPI: STEP-LEAVE-100 submit UC-LEAVE-APPROVE
    ApprovalAPI->>LeaveTable: STEP-LEAVE-110 update request status approved
    ApprovalAPI->>ApprovalTable: STEP-LEAVE-110 insert approval action
    ApprovalAPI->>EventBus: STEP-LEAVE-120 emit approved event
    EventBus-->>Employee: STEP-LEAVE-140 notification generated
